Domain Mode with cluster:

1.Add user
cd /bin ./add-user.bat

userName:ajeethkumar
password:ajeethkumar*1

Generated key
<secret value="YWplZXRoa3VtYXIqMQ==" />


Need to add interface in host-master.xml

<interface name="public">
	<inet-address value="${jboss.bind.address:127.0.0.1}"/>
</interface>
<interface name="unsecure">
<inet-address value="${jboss.bind.address:127.0.0.1}"/>
</interface>


Run using this cmd:  cd bin
	./domain.sh  --host-config=host-master.xml



---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
jboss slave:

secret key added in host-slave.xml

run using this cmd:
 ./domain.sh --host-config=host-slave.xml -Djboss.domain.master.address=127.0.0.1


Error facing :java.net.BindException: Already in use 127.0.0.1:1990 so in change to 1991 in host-slave.xml






